                  <li><strong>PII</strong>: Personally Identifiable Information (name, email, etc.)</li>
                  <li><strong>Sensitive</strong>: Special category data requiring additional protection</li>
                  <li><strong>Non-PII</strong>: Data that doesn't identify individuals</li>
                  <li><strong>Anonymous</strong>: Data safe for use in pre-qualification</li>
