          <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
            <li>Navigate to the lead record</li>
            <li>Click <strong>Compliance</strong> > <strong>Consent</strong></li>
            <li>View the list of consent records</li>
            <li>Click on a specific consent record to see details:
